 8. the person playing domino is in an even position##4
 9. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the japanese##3
10. the person playing snooker is the italian##1
11. the person eating broccoli is between the person eating spinach and the person playing domino##2
12. the person playing bridge is the person eating raspberry##1

