.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, july, april
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, mystery, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, colombian, french, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, rowing, skateboarding, soccer
 1. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the brazilian is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5
 4. the french is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the left of the french##5
 6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the colombian##3
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's sport is rowing##7
 8. the person who's birthday is in april is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
 9. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
10. the person watching action movies is on the left of the french##1
11. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |       4       |
| Birthday         | september      | january   | april   | july       |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action    | disaster | mystery       |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | colombian | french   | malaysian     |
| Sport         | baseball   | soccer    | rowing   | skateboarding |

