.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, soy-milk, water
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, chess, filmmaking
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, ritmeester, old-henry, cain
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, funk, indie, rock
 1. the person drinking fanta is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 2. the fan of electronic is between the person who's hobby is chess and the dunhill-smoker##2
 3. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the fan of funk is not the old-henry-smoker##6
 7. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the person who's hobby is filmmaking and the person who's hobby is board-games##7
 8. the fan of electronic is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
 9. the cain-smoker is not the person who's hobby is filmmaking##6
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
11. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of rock##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is not the person drinking fanta##6
13. the old-henry-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
14. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
15. the ritmeester-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Beverage      | fanta      | 7up        | water          | soy-milk    |
| Hobby         | filmmaking | camping    | chess          | board-games |
| Cigar           | dunhill  | ritmeester   | old-henry | cain      |
| Music-Genre   | rock       | electronic | indie          | funk        |

